Harry Ford (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harry_Ford_(actor) 0 Harry Ford (born 1983) is an American actor. He starred in the CBS medical drama Code Black as third-year resident Dr. Angus Leighton. Harry Ford ( born 1983 ) is an_American_actor .
